snippet.title: Thelma Thrift
snippet.description:
Ebay PowerSeller & Special Education teacher: I THRIFT shop for fashion, JEWELRY  luxury, and designer items to resell or to keep. Ride Along with me to thrift shops, estate sales, garage sales. We may unbox a Louis Vuitton one day, or ship my latest sales for Ebay, Poshmark, Etsy, and Amazon. I love vlogging which can include jaunts here and there or, maybe I'll cook something delicious, in addition, I share tips that earned me Ebay's, prestigious, "Power Seller" $tatu$

Please subscribe, comment, and share my videos.
